In addition the Midlands Industrial Council also paid £5,000 for a survey in Westmorland & Lonsdale Lib-Dem - Lib-Dem hold.

Also donations totalling £571,000 were paid to Conservative Central Office and Head Office.

Cash donations to constituency associations total: £382,289.95 plus £2,500 to the Conservatives in Hertfordshire.
